Package etomica.osmoticvirial

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AshtonWildingLJ
    Extends Ashton and Wilding approach for calculation of gas virial coefficient to Lennard-Jones model.
    AshtonWildingLJ.simParams  
    AshtonWildingOsmoticVirial
    Implements Ashton and Wilding method for calculation of osmotic virial coefficient (B2, B3) for Hard-Sphere model as described in the paper DOI: 10.1063/1.4883718.
    AshtonWildingOsmoticVirial.simParams  
    AshtonWildingVirial
    Implements Ashton and Wilding method for calculation of gas virial coefficients (B2, B3) for Hard-Sphere model as described in the paper DOI: 10.1063/1.4883718.
    AshtonWildingVirial.simParams  
    GCRestrictedGibbsHS
    Calculate osmotic virial coefficients for Hard-Sphere potential in Grand Canonical ensemble for solvent from Free-Energy Perturbation Approach in restricted grand canonical ensemble
    GCRestrictedGibbsHS.simParams  
    GCWidomInsertHS
    Calculate osmotic virial coefficients for Hard-Sphere potential in Grand Canonical ensemble for solvent from Free-Energy Perturbation Approach utilizing Widom's Insertion.
    GCWidomInsertHS.simParams  
    IntegratorRGEMC
    Simple Gibbs-ensemble Monte Carlo integrator.
    MCMoveGeometricCluster
    Implementation of geometric cluster move of Liu and Luijten.
    MCMoveGeometricClusterRestrictedGE
    Implementation of geometric cluster move for restricted gibbs ensemble by Liu, Luijten and Wilding.
    MCMoveListenerRGE  
    MeterRmin
    Calculates minimum pair distance from all the possible pairs of atoms as required by Ashton and Wilding's method
    MeterRminSpecies
    Calculates minimum pair distance from all the possible pairs of atoms of a particular species as required by Ashton and Wilding's method
    NVTWidomInsertLJ
    Calculate osmotic virial coefficients for Lennard-Jones potential in Canonical ensemble from Free-Energy Perturbation Approach utilizing Widom's Insertion.
    NVTWidomInsertLJ.simParams  
    PotentialDepletion
